title: Veg Out
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Pizza, International, Fast food, Take-out
description: Small veggie cafe with counter service that caters to mostly the locals. Menu features a variety of choices from pizza, salads, and wraps, to veggieburgers, main plates, pizza, to fresh carrot juice. Has vegan cakes. Food is served on disposable and take-out ware in a simple space.
